    • Method Detail

      • open

        public boolean open()
        Tries to open the current selection. If there is no selection, there is no effect. If the selection is a directory, the window is refreshed to show its contents. If the selection is a file, the function returns false, indicating that the window should be hidden and the result queried.
        Returns:
        false if the selection is a file and browsing should be terminated, true otherwise
